## Usage

### 1. Build the agent image

```bash
kagent build {{.Name}} --push
```

### 2. Deploy the agent

**Option A: Direct API key**
```bash
kagent deploy {{.Name}} --api-key <your-api-key>
```
**Option B: Using Kubernetes secret**
```bash
Create secret
kubectl create secret generic my-secret -n <namespace>
--from-literal={{.ModelProvider | upper}}_API_KEY=$API_KEY
--dry-run=client -o yaml | kubectl apply -f -

Deploy with secret
kagent deploy {{.Name}} --api-key-secret "my-secret"
```
